      • updateRegistrationStatus

        public ResponseDTO updateRegistrationStatus(List<PacketStatusDTO> exportedPackets)
        Description copied from interface: PacketExportService
        Updates the exported packet status in the Registration table

        The following columns in the Registration table will be updated based on the packet uploaded to server.

        • Client Status Code
        • File Upload Status
        • Client Status Comment
        • Upload Count
        • Server Status Code

        Returns the status of the virus scan as ResponseDTO object.

        If virus scan has completed successfully, SuccessResponseDTO will be set in ResponseDTO object

        If any exception occurs, ErrorResponseDTO will be set in ResponseDTO object

        Specified by:
        updateRegistrationStatus in interface PacketExportService
        Parameters:
        exportedPackets - The list of exported packets
        Returns:
        Return the response based on the success or failure response
